[00:09.91]Remember again
[00:13.83]magenta
[00:16.21]作曲/編曲：ダルビッシュP
[00:19.51]作詞：ナノ(nano)
[00:22.60]唄：ナノ(nano)
[00:25.31]by：Yuria
[00:32.77]Inside a world of broken words you cannot hide　ひび割れた言葉の世界で
[00:42.44]you try to find the reasons why, as days collide　ひたすら理由を探し続ける
[00:52.11]the seconds keep on passing, without a sound, you turn around　一秒一秒が過ぎていく中で　音も無く君は去った
[00:57.12]and as you walk away I call to you　その孤独な背中に僕は呼びかけた
[01:01.52][02:02.07][03:41.20]Don't you let go　手放さないで
[01:03.62][03:23.49]take a look around, you are not alone　君は独りじゃない
[01:06.44][03:26.03]if you'd only stop and close your eyes　ただ目を開けば
[01:09.00][03:28.54]find the answers, you'd find the answers　答えは見つかるはず
[01:11.55][02:12.15][03:31.17][03:51.33]when you feel like the world if falling in　この世界が崩れて
[01:14.17][03:33.82]and you can't seem to find the way back in　帰る場所を失ったとしても
[01:16.80][03:36.36][03:56.54]don't cry　泣かないで
[01:19.41][02:20.09][03:59.21]just hear these words and remember again　この言葉に耳をすませて思い出して
[01:33.46]Outside, you're trembling as you stand, in the falling rain　雨の中震えながら立ちすくみ
[01:43.46]you try to find where you belong, as you drown the pain　行くべき場所を探しながら 雨が痛みを流してくれた
[01:52.79]You hear the voices crying inside a world monochrome　モノクロの世界の中で聞こえた泣き声
[01:57.96]but their eyes are bleeding tears of magenta　でも流れた涙はマジェンタだった
[02:04.51][03:43.73]take another breath when you're lost again　行き場を見失った時、ただ呼吸をして
[02:07.17][03:46.27]if you'd only break the walls within　その壁を壊した先には
[02:09.63][03:48.75]find the courage, you'd find the courage　勇気が潜んでいるはず
[02:14.77][03:54.07]and you can't seem to find the way back in 　帰る場所を失ったとしても
[02:17.35]don't cry 　泣かないで
[02:23.96]Another silent prayer fades as the night slips past　夜明けが訪れま一つの祈りが消え去る
[02:34.11]I try to reach out to the light through the glass as it shatters　砕けた硝子の向こうの光に触れた気がした
[03:21.06]Don't you let go 　手放さないで
[03:38.81]just hear these words and remember　この言葉に耳をすませて思い出して
